line.

00:04:38.569 --> 00:04:41.309
Wherever you're going look ahead a little
bit.

00:04:41.309 --> 00:04:46.069
A good driver will always look ahead,
you don't look directly what's in front of

00:04:46.069 --> 00:04:48.169
you because..
you'll have a crash!

